ntain Pose C h a i r Ta d a s a n a 2.";i:44;s:21:"Chair Neck Rolls A 3.";i:45;s:21:"Chair Neck Rolls B 4.";i:46;s:21:"Chair Neck Rolls C 5.";i:47;s:32:"Seated Cactus Arms Flow Chair 6.";i:48;s:26:"Standing Shoulder Rolls 7.";i:49;s:33:"Chair Seated Side Stretch Pose 8.";i:50;s:26:"Chair Seated Side Stretch.";i:51;s:43:"Todays Pose - Lunge Twisted Lunge Benefits.";i:52;s:73:"Lunge bend extend - Stretches the hips hamstrings hip flexors and groins.";i:53;s:56:"Strengthens the 1min Chair Yoga - Part 1 Lunge on Vimeo.";i:54;s:67:"Sit tall in a chair and extend straight arms up inhaling as you go.";i:55;s:87:"As you exhale twist your torso to the left and place your right hand on your left knee.";i:56;s:67:"Reach your left arm behind you placing it on the back of the chair.";i:57;s:115:"Breathe in deeply getting longer through the spine and as you exhale see if you can increase the twist more gently.";i:58;s:32:"Yoga chair poses and stretching.";i:59;s:122:"Woman sitting on chair and stretching to touch her toes Koldunov Getty Images You know you need to sit less and move more.";i:60;s:67:"But what if at the very least you could move while you were seated.";i:61;s:18:"It is a wise idea.";i:62;s:47:"When you stretch or move frequently throughout.";i:63;s:148:"Chair yoga is an ideal exercise for those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain carpal tunnel syndrome osteoporosis and multiple sclerosis.";i:64;s:122:"It may also benefit people over a certain age who have trouble moving through the up and down motions of traditional yoga.";i:65;s:42:"Chair yoga allows them to stay stabilized.";i:66;s:30:"Stand behind or to side chair.";i:67;s:19:"Take hold of chair.";i:68;s:25:"Step back with left foot.";i:69;s:24:"Drop left knee to floor.";i:70;s:20:"Repeat on other leg.";i:71;s:73:"Alana shares a dynamic variation of downward dog and lunges with a chair.";i:72;s:158:"This sequence is designed to assist yogis get up-and-down from the floor promoting increased mobility and flexibility in the hamstrings thighs hips and spine.";i:73;s:66:"If standing lunges arent right for your body try a seated version.";i:74;s:65:"Sit tall in a chair with your knees toes and hips facing forward.";i:75;s:108:"Open your knees and thighs out to the right and left with your knees facing the same direction as your toes.";i:76;s:125:"TraceeYoga- Easy Chair Yoga for Beginners Video Description A short beginners yoga practice done entirely sitting in a chair.";i:77;s:90:"Perfect for beginners people with injuries or people with difficulty getting on the floor.";i:78;s:59:"Timeless Yoga - Jennifer Warnock is at Resound Yoga Studio.";i:79;s:26:"Is at Resound Yoga Studio.";}}